528
00:50:13,300 --> 00:50:16,000
Girls in white dresses
With blue satin sashes

529
00:50:16,300 --> 00:50:19,500
Snowflakes that stay
On my nose and eyelashes

530
00:50:19,700 --> 00:50:22,800
Silver white winters
That melt into springs

531
00:50:23,100 --> 00:50:26,400
These are a few of my favorite things

532
00:50:26,700 --> 00:50:28,300
When the dog bites

533
00:50:28,500 --> 00:50:30,200
When the bee stings

534
00:50:30,500 --> 00:50:32,700
When I'm feeling sad

535
00:50:33,000 --> 00:50:36,400
I simply remember my favorite things

536
00:50:36,600 --> 00:50:43,500
And then I don 't feel so bad

537
00:50:44,200 --> 00:50:45,900
-Does it work?
-Of course.

538
00:50:46,100 --> 00:50:48,100
-What do you like?
-Pussy willow!

539
00:50:48,800 --> 00:50:51,100
-Christmas!
-Bunny rabbits!

540
00:50:51,300 --> 00:50:52,900
Snakes!

541
00:50:53,200 --> 00:50:55,400
-Chocolate icing!
-No school!

542
00:50:55,600 --> 00:50:56,800
Pillow fights!

543
00:50:57,100 --> 00:50:59,100
-Telegrams!
-Birthday presents!

544
00:50:59,400 --> 00:51:01,800
-Any presents!
-Ladybugs!

545
00:51:03,300 --> 00:51:04,700
A good sneeze!

546
00:51:04,900 --> 00:51:06,700
Gesundheit!

547
00:51:06,900 --> 00:51:08,200
See what fun it is?

