00:52:03,800 --> 00:52:05,100
Hello.

564
00:52:05,300 --> 00:52:09,500
Fräulein, did I not tell you that
bedtime is to be strictly observed?

565
00:52:09,700 --> 00:52:12,500
The children were upset
by the storm, so l--

566
00:52:13,800 --> 00:52:14,800
You did, sir.

567
00:52:15,100 --> 00:52:19,300
Do you, or do you not, have difficulty
remembering such simple instructions?

568
00:52:20,600 --> 00:52:22,200
Only during thunderstorms.

569
00:52:24,700 --> 00:52:26,200
Liesl?

570
00:52:26,400 --> 00:52:28,700
I don't recall seeing you
after dinner.

571
00:52:29,200 --> 00:52:31,000
Really? As a matter of fact--

572
00:52:31,200 --> 00:52:32,400
Yes?

573
00:52:33,300 --> 00:52:34,400
Well, I was--

574
00:52:34,700 --> 00:52:36,800
What she would like to say. . .

575
00:52:37,000 --> 00:52:39,800
. . .is that she and I have
been getting acquainted tonight.

576
00:52:40,100 --> 00:52:44,900
It's too late to go into that. You
heard your father. Go back to bed.

577
00:52:49,600 --> 00:52:51,000
Fräulein. . .

578
00:52:51,300 --> 00:52:55,300
. . .you have managed to remember
I'm leaving in the morning?

579
00:52:56,400 --> 00:53:01,000
Is it also possible you remember the
first rule in this house is discipline?

580
00:53:02,600 --> 00:53:05,100
Then I trust that before I return. . .

581
00:53:05,600 --> 00:53:07,400
. . .you'll have acquired some?

582
00:53:08,800 --> 00:53:10,200
Captain?

583
00:53:11,100 --> 00:53:15,000
Could I talk to you about clothes
for the children for when they play?

584
00:53:15,200 --> 00:53:18,000
-If I could have some material.
-You are many things.

585
00:53:18,200 --> 00:53:20,400
Not the least of which is repetitious.

586
00:53:20,600 --> 00:53:22,800
-But they're children!
-Yes.

587
00:53:23,000 --> 00:53:24,800
And I'm their father.

588
00:53:25,400 --> 00:53:26,600
Good night.

